                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010701-17-off98 t18010701-17-cd99"></join>, on hundred and thirty-seven yards of corded dimity, value 16l. 3s. 6d. two hundred and eighteen yards of muslinet, value 27l. 1s. 8d. and two yards of wrapper, value 2s. the property of 
                     
