                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010701-17-defend182 t18010701-17-punish102"></join>
               Death
            </rs>, aged 28.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Rooke.</p>
